title: NO-FEE Modern 2 Bed 2 Bath in Hudson Yards! Plus Free Rent!
posting_body: ['NO-FEE Modern 2 Bed 2 Bath in Hudson Yards!', 'Listing ID #: 138513', 'Price: $7,434', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 2.0', 'Bathrooms: 2.0', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Subway', 'Laundry', 'Bicycle Room', 'Storage', 'Roof Deck', 'Wheelchair Access', 'Receiving Room', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood', 'Light', 'NO FEE', 'Laundry In Unit', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'This no-fee, beautiful 2 bed 2 bath offers condo-level finishes, a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a spa-like bathroom with Italian porcelain tiling, oak wood flooring, chrome fixtures, oversized windows, individually controlled heat & air, and an in-home washer & dryer.', 'This luxury building offers a 24-hour doorman, expansive solarium and sky lounge with private cabanas, squash court, fitness center, co-working spaces, golf simulator, pet washing room, bike & resident storage, valet services, and Caffe Vento on site.', 'Conveniently located near the 7/A/C/E/ W 39th St Ferry.', 'Note: Listed rent is net effective based on 1 month free.', 'Gross rent is $8,110.', 'LISTING #138513', 'Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'New York Living Solutions - Keller Williams New York City \xa0 201-350-7865 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Sabrina Rosal at 201-350-7865']
